      <link href="https://pre-commit.com/#hooks-pass_filenames">pre-commit: pass_filenames flag for graph-aware tools.</link>
      <link href="https://github.com/microsoft/TypeScript/wiki/Performance#using---noemit">TypeScript: --noEmit and project references.</link>
      <link href="https://docs.astral.sh/ruff/configuration/#using-ruff-in-pre-commit">Astral: ruff in pre-commit (staged-list semantics).</link>
    </see-also>
  </content>
</methodology>
